<hl>
<seg id=1> Huanghe "Golden Three Corners " becoming a new popular place for investment. </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Taiyuan, February 7th, by Baohong Shan and trainee Xianguo Hu - Located at the boards of Shanxi, Shaanxi and Henan provinces in China, Fenglindu economic development zone, also called Huanghe "Golden Three Corners" is increasingly attracting attentions from the domestic merchants and oversea investors, and becoming a new popular place for investment. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> Fenglindu economic developing zone is the only one developing zone that relies on small counties in China.  It is also the new passageway for Shanxi, an inland province to open up to the outside. </seg>
<seg id=4> After three years construction, this developing zone has begun forming its basic scale as an integrated multiple wholesale market for the commodity circulation of wood, medicine, tobaccos, clothing, food and industrial products. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=5> At present, a forest of storied buildings and commercial buildings come together in crowds inside this developing zone--the construction of  "Golden Three Corners" village is at its end of process. Two thousand telephones have been used, and a ten thousand watt high voltage power generating system is under regular operation which has attracted many investors, the products from more than thirty factories such as Lemon factory, the perfume factory, special painting factory and ect. are transported to all corners of the inland region. The new hospitals with advanced medical equipments specialize in setting bones, gynecology and pediatric care have been open for business. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> The rapid development inside "Golden Three Corners" has drawn the attention of the overseas merchants. Thirty-one projects are currently in the process of negotiation by more than fifty financial groups from US, France, Japan, Korea Taiwan and other countries or regions, the total amount of the foreign investment has reached 320 million Yuan. </seg>
</p>
